; dw.size: S(1,2), M(3), B(4,5) --> 1-3
; dw.age: N(1,2),M(3,4),O(5,6)  --> 1-3


; 2018.07.16
; Min Gas consumption  9.2
; Min Elec consumption 1000
; dw.age 1-3 ==> 1,3,5 (to provide middle classes)]]></code>
